  {
    "hotel_id": "297968",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/conrad-macao-cotai-central/hotel/macau-mo.html",
    "name": "Conrad Macao",
    "detail": "i was impressed... let's look at how: 1) taking my first steps into the hotel, i wasn't greeted with pungent high-class-wanna be fragrance. it was subtle yet pleasant. 2) unlike most hotels in macau, conrad is targetting high end clients. you don't see the same congested crowd of villagers from mainland china who tend to squad around the lobbies, scream off the top of their lungs for a normal conversation, and people rubbing their toes in public. this hotel was classy (i hope it stays that way). 3) they surprised me with a free upgrade to a suite. i was welcomed by friendly smiles and staff who were eager to help and provide good service (not the type who are overly eager). 4) all the staff i encountered were attentive and responsive. i have stayed at several different hotels in macau including new establishments. this was by far my best experience. i cannot wait to go back for another visit.",
